videos.description: Kansas State's Alex Barnes takes the handoff to the outside and rushes for a 27-yard gain.
videos.headline: Barnes finds opening for long gain

videos.description: Kansas State's Skylar Thompson tries connecting with Byron Pringle but is picked off by UCLA's Darnay Holmes in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Holmes forces Thompson's 1st INT

videos.description: Kansas State's Alex Delton finds an opening up the middle and rushes for a 68-yard touchdown on his first play replacing Skylar Thompson at quarterback.
videos.headline: Delton breaks free for long TD run

videos.description: UCLA's Devon Modster finds Jordan Lasley for the phenomenal two-handed catch in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Lasley reels in incredible catch

videos.description: UCLA's Devon Modster links up with Jordan Lasley for a 52-yard touchdown reception.
videos.headline: Modster connects with Lasley for TD

videos.description: UCLA's Devon Modster sends a ball deep over the middle to Theo Howard for the long 70-yard touchdown reception.
videos.headline: Modster finds Howard wide open for 2nd TD pass

videos.description: Kansas State's Isaiah Zuber takes the option handoff and rushes for a 37-yard gain in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Zuber breaks out for big gain on option

videos.description: Kansas State's Alex Delton rushes up the middle and is assisted by a few linemen pushing him in for a 1-yard score.
videos.headline: Delton converts big 4th down with rushing TD

videos.description: UCLA's Bolu Olorunfunmi attempts to rush up the middle but is stripped by Kansas State's Denzel Goolsby to force a turnover.
videos.headline: Goolsby strips Olorunfunmi for key turnover

videos.description: Kansas State's Alex Delton finds Dominque Heath on the outside for a 8-yard touchdown to give the Wildcats the lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Heath shakes off defender for TD

videos.description: Kansas State's Alex Barnes rushes up the middle and breaks a tackle on the 41-yard touchdown to extend the lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Barnes' TD extends Wildcats lead

videos.description: Kansas State's Alex Delton takes the draw up the middle for a 3-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Delton rushes for 3rd TD

videos.description: Playing without Josh Rosen, UCLA falls to Kansas State 35-17, with the Wildcats rushing for 344 yards and four scores.
videos.headline: Kansas State rolls past UCLA in Cactus Bowl
